<h2>Odessa Jira – Internal Demo Tracker</h2>

<p>
    <strong>Odessa Jira</strong> is an internal tool for tracking demo Jira items.
</p>

<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Projects:</strong> Create and manage demo projects (e.g., <em>Stellantis Demo – STLA</em>).</li>
    <li><strong>Boards:</strong> Organize projects into boards (e.g., <em>STLA – Auto Servicing</em>).</li>
    <li><strong>Work Items:</strong> Add tasks, stories, or bugs under boards.</li>
    <li><strong>Status Configuration:</strong> Define workflows (e.g., To Do, In Progress, Done).</li>
</ul>

<p>
    <strong>Purpose:</strong> Track demo work items efficiently for internal teams.
</p>

<p>
    <em>For internal use only</em>
</p>
